author: Whitney Medworth
title: John Wall threw a perfect between-the-legs pass on a fast break
text: Rec The Wizards are rolling. One week ago today, the played one in one of the greatest regular season games in NBA history. They fell to the Cavaliers that night but it gave us an idea of how good the Wizards could be. This Monday? They’re destroying the Russell Westbrook led Oklahoma City Thunder . John Wall is having an absolute blast on the court doing it as well. Completing one of his favorite pass attempts, he went between-the-legs on this fast break and it was beautiful. Just moments before that, he had made another great pass to Otto Porter . — Washington Wizards (@WashWizards) February 14, 2017 John Wall having fun means great things for the Wizards.
